[04:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Hydream Oven uses the Scalist prompting framework, which means if you use too many commas or text style prompts, the model will get confused. So, our next step is fixing the skin'

[04:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'completely. And the question arises, how can we do that? And to fix that, we have to write a prompt that is supported by this model. You must write your prompt in the'

[04:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Scalist format, which stands for subject, composition, action, location, image style, specs, and text. This is the full form of Scalist. Now, you have to write in this exact'

